title: Kate Winslet, Meryl Streep & Carey Mulligan Bring Star Power To Elle's Women In Hollywood Awards 2015!
text: Kate Winslet, Meryl Streep and Carey Mulligan keep it chic and sophisticated while attending the 2015 Elle Women in Hollywood Awards held at the Four Seasons Los Angeles at Beverly Hills on Monday (October 19) in Beverly Hills, Calif.
